  "page_help": "Caasimad & FAQ",
  "help_system_title": "📋 Sharaxad Nidaamka",
  "help_system_desc1": "FastWrite waa qalab halka ah loo adeegsan karaa soo qaybinta otomaatig data dukumiinti (invoices, hantida, vouchers) iyadoo adhi dhalaalaynta (AI). Waxaa ah sida loo adeegsan solo kumaalaakuugan — datakaaga ma la wadaagayo mid kale oo dhan, kaas oo ay ku jira maamulaha platform-ka.",
  "help_system_desc2": "Waxa waxaa lagu samayaa: Aad diriri kartaa PDF iyadoo leh mid ama qaar badan invoices. Nidaamka otomaatig waxaa lagu aqoonsadaa kasta invoice gaarka ah, lagu ogaadaa hormood, la beddalaa calaamuunka saxda ah, soo qaybtaa data aad ku sharteesay (invoice number, date, amounts, line items, etc.). Dhamaadkii, aad dhaafin kartaa natiijaada CSV ama Excel.",
  "help_workflow_title": "🔄 Socdaalka Shaqo — Billoowga ku jiidda Billowga",
  "help_step1_title": "Qaab Furahka API",
  "help_step1_desc": "Tag Tixraafo → Furaha API oo galya furahkaaga AI (sida Google Gemini). Tan waa looga yaabaa — platform-ka ma bixisa furahkiisa. Laabashisha waxaa lagu samayaa toos ah akoonkaaga AI.",
  "help_step2_title": "Diriri Dukumiinti",
  "help_step2_desc": "Tag Diriri & Quto. Jiidya ama dooro fayl PDF (ilaa 200 invoices isbitiga fayl) oo lamaantay \"Diiwaangeliya Dukumiinti\". Nidaamka otomaatig waxaa lagu ogaadaa invoices gaarka ah hormood.",
  "help_step3_title": "Samee Calaamuunka",
  "help_step3_desc": "Ka bogaadka Dukumiinti, dooro mid ama qaar badan dukumiinti oo lamaantay \"Calaamuunka\". Waxaa lagu geeri doonaa bogaad gaar ah halka aad dukumiinti dhab ah aragto bidix iyo form calaamuunka midig. Ka qeex beelka la raba aad soo qaatid (sida invoice number, date, total, VAT) iyo line items. Ama, samee calaamuunka bogaadka Calaamuunka → + Calaamuunka Cusub.",
  "help_step4_title": "Soo Qubinta Data (Batch)",
  "help_step4_desc": "Ka bogaadka Dukumiinti, dooro dukumiinti oo lamaantay \"Batch\". Nidaamka waxaa loo adeegsan karaa AI lagu soo qaytid data abadka calaamuunka dukumiinti kasta. Natiijaada waxaa ay muujiyaan tableeka dukumiinti.",
  "help_step5_title": "Eegid & Oggolasha",
  "help_step5_desc": "Ka bogaadka Dukumiinti, dooro dukumiinti oo lamaantay \"Oggolasha\". Aad aragta invoice bidix iyo data soo qaatay midig. Hagiya khaladka midkood oo lamaantay \"Oggolasha Invoice\". Iftiinka isku xidh iftiinka xariirka dukumiinti markaad ku socoto safu.",
  "help_step6_title": "Dhaaf Faylal",
  "help_step6_desc": "Marka dukumiinti oggolashay, socoddhigaag bogaadka Dukumiinti. Dooro dukumiinti oggolashay oo lamaantay \"CSV\", \"XLSX\" ama \"Line Items XLSX\" lagu dhaafin. Haddii midna la doortayn, dukumiinti oggolashay oo dhan waxaa lagu dhaafin.",
  "help_tip_title": "💡 Talo",
  "help_tip_text": "Dalboorta saxda ah: Diriri → Calaamuunka → Batch → Oggolasha → Dhaaf. Ugu horay samee calaamuunka kasta nooca invoice (sida DEI, COSMOTE, VODAFONE) kahor biloowga soo qaybinta caasimad. Marka aad sameeyo calaamuunka, nidaamka otomaatig waxaa la beddalaa invoices cusub hormood la mid ah.",
  "help_faq_title": "❓ Su'aalaha Inta Badan Wasaleyda",
  "help_faq_search": "🔍 Raadi su'aalo...",
